alt_text: a simple rectangular aquarium made in roblox. the aquarium has a sandy substrate, some plants in the corners of the tank, and a piece of driftwood in the center. two kuhli loaches are present, one underneath the driftwood and one hiding in some plants. a honey gourami is swimming near the top of the water, and a chinese mystery snail is in the back of the tank.
